@node "UNDER PRESSURE"
UNDER PRESSURE

Type "GRYMALIN" and 'F1' now skips levels while pressing '1' - '9' gives
different weapons.
@endnode
@node "UNREAL"
UNREAL

On the animation screen with the 3D balls, type "ORDILOGICUS" and hit
'Return'.  The screen should flash white or colors.  You now have unlimited
energy on the next play.  Skip levels by pressing 'Return'.
@endnode
@node "UNTOUCHABLES"
UNTOUCHABLES

When the title screen appears while loading, type in "SOUTHAMPTON GAZETTE"
(Note may have no space between two words) and the screen flashes to indicate
cheat mode.  Press 'F10' to skip levels.
       
Pressing 'HELP' on levels 2, 3, and 6 to warp to the second half of the level.

Another cheat: Pause the game then type these codes to skip levels:

       1 - Bride Rolls
       2 - Mac N Alley
       3 - Kid Zapping
       4 - A Nit in Time
@endnode
@node "VAXINE"
VAXINE

While playing type "WILDEBEESTE".  Now use these Function keys to skip levels.

   'F1'  - Advance one level
   'F2'  - Retreat one level
   'F3'  - Advance ten levels
   'F4'  - Retreat ten levels
   'F10' - Advance one level and get a bonus.
@endnode  
