@node "VIGILANTE"
VIGILANTE

Enter your name as "GREEN CRYSTAL" (with space) or "POOKY IS MY PAL" into the
high score table then in-game pressing 'F1' will give you extra lives and
'F8' will advance you a level.

Enter your name as "POOKY IS MY PAL" in the highscore table, and now 'F1' 
will increase your lives, and 'F8' goes to the next level.
@endnode
